message.hero-message: Create, Edit, and Securely Save Your Resume Right on Our Platform, Even on Your Phone!
message.highlight-title: Not Just a Resume Builder, But a Platform!
message.highlight-message: We are an all-encompassing platform that connects non-LaTeX writers with LaTeX writers by providing incentives for them to share professional templates.
message.highlight-free: The platform is accessible at no cost.
message.highlight-hidden-cost: Unlike our competitor, we do not impose a subscription service on our customers. Our paid template, in addition to our "Free Template", is only a one-time fee, allowing us to give back to the LaTeX writing community.
message.highlight-privacy: We understand the importance of data privacy and make it our mission to protect it.
message.cloud-storage-message-1: With Cloudsumé, you no longer need to store your resumes on file-hosting services.
message.cloud-storage-message-2: You can also update your resumes whenever you want, including on your smartphone, without the need to download any additional apps.
message.switch-template-title: Change The Template Anytime You Want
message.switch-template-message: Giving your resume a new look is as simple as a few clicks; by changing the template, you can create a new resume with all of your information intact.
message.much-more-message: Create a link to share your resume, share common data between resumes, use a country-awareness template, and take advantage of other features to help you create the perfect resume.
message.latex-author-title: Do you know how to create LaTeX documents?
message.latex-author-message: Join our community and earn a passive income by creating a resume template that will assist people all over the world in landing their dream job.

message.guest-signout-warning: You will lose access to all of your resumes forever if you sign out. However, any links to share your resume that you have created will continue to work but you will not be able to delete those links. Do you want to sign out? This action cannot be UNDONE!
